{"tid":1244981,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對於6月21號既行動 我有少少野想講","createTime":"2019-06-20T06:45:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T07:00:54.000Z","uid":243158,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"cd9d40929f1e7e52b6d1b8661c2a97c3a9d5d9de","tid":1244981,"uid":243158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:45:05.000Z","msg":"首先 我係企係大家個邊 都認同政府要撤回條例 同埋要追究黑警 並唔係要分化大家 但係啱啱同完唔同人傾 發現大家都想抖抖 唔係因為想縮 而係無論體力上 抑或經濟上都要俾大家恢復下元氣 呢批人既年紀都係30-50 都係一批有事業基礎 有家庭負擔既一班人 始終無得罷咁耐工 當然佢地好多謝成班年青人為成個香港社會發聲 但係都希望你地諒解下佢地 佢地好明白大家唔想辜負義士既遺願 亦想乘勝追擊 食住個勢 但係假如大家唔顧及下上面批人既話 恐怕好快會出現一個分歧 香港加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6da2f267dd0d2ee9e9cc6cf7636f5aef0cb0025","tid":1244981,"uid":207702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:48:06.000Z","msg":"去左先講"},{"pid":"2838706619f0e557e4b5d34f3d00ba751e75908d","tid":1244981,"uid":243158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6da2f267dd0d2ee9e9cc6cf7636f5aef0cb0025","tid":1244981,"uid":207702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:48:06.000Z","msg":"去左先講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T06:53:40.000Z","msg":"出一定會出 只係希望大家可以體諒一下我地"},{"pid":"6ba7f8930db339e2be759884c34d3d47a90e2dbd","tid":1244981,"uid":156936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-20T07:00:54.000Z","msg":"【請為621廣泛報料，聽朝七點，政總集合】<br />\n立法會、政總、警總、禮賓府警察勢力分報圖，持續收料，一直更新。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5rtOBOy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5rtOBOy.jpg&h=eae4919c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歡迎加入討論: <strong>圖解香港禮賓府旅遊路線</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1241712/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1241712/page/1</a><br />\n<strong>更多細節請用追故模式</strong><br />\n===============================<br />\n夢見好多人想開放日遊覽禮賓府。<br />\n但聽聞條斜路好危險，驚人多出現意外。<br />\n為安全著想，出席任何活動前，<span style=\"color: red;\">大家都有義務了解該地環境</span>，<br />\n希望各位唔好一知半解的情況下跟隨人流，造成危險。<br />\n===============================<br />\n禮賓府高空、地則及2018香港地圖懶人包<br />\n===============================<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uc7zysM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUc7zysM.jpg&h=48f9f43a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C6aA1c0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC6aA1c0.jpg&h=0cd9b552&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eTyu5EG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeTyu5EG.jpg&h=9be2896f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n禮賓府交通路線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pZoOuRy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpZoOuRy.jpg&h=6ca9e50d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5v6z9Rz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5v6z9Rz.jpg&h=7291e991&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n====================<br />\n禮賓府建議地鐵步行路線<br />\n====================<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JUqEBwz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJUqEBwz.jpg&h=f978913f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n===============<br />\n禮賓府地下通道新聞<br />\n===============<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ceZBDKW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FceZBDKW.jpg&h=7ac3a5fb&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓主現時收集以下的資料及圖片，作學術研究之用 :<br />\n<del>1. 禮賓府正確的出入口和閘門總數(己達成)</del><br />\n<del>2. 禮賓府旁舊樓梯及非行車小徑等Google Map無法標示之通道(己達成)</del><br />\n3. 急救站、飲水機、洗手間或可設立急救站空地等休息位置<br />\n4. 立法會、政總、警總、禮賓府野生犬隻出沒或聚居地點 (可以Google map mark比我最好)<br />\n<del>5. 由蘭桂坊或香港動植物公園前往的最佳路線(己達成)</del><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[同我推晒佢] 力抗膠post 621行動討論整合</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1242813/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1242813/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後，立法會、政總、警總、禮賓府全部都相當有歷史價值，係一家大細親子好去處，大家記得要遵守秩序，<span style=\"color: red;\">去之前記得做足功課</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />平時無開放千奇唔好去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}